{"id":151828,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/google游说内华达允许自主驾驶汽车上路/","date":"2011-05-12T04:30:47Z","modified":"2011-05-12T04:30:47Z","title":"Google游说内华达允许自主驾驶汽车上路","content":"<p>自主驾驶汽车的先锋Google，正悄悄游说内华达州立法允许合法驾驶此类汽车。 Google去年承认它的自主驾驶汽车，在加州的公路上行驶了超过14万英里，其中超过1千英里是完全无人干预的。当时Google并没有披露多少商业企图。本周二，Google证实它正在游说立法允许自主驾驶汽车上路。公司发言人表示，该项目仍然处于测试阶段。Google雇佣了赌城的一位说客，推动内华达州通过两项法案。其一是电动汽车修正案，向自主驾驶汽车颁发测试执照。其二是增加一条豁免，允许驾驶中发短信。对于完全自主驾驶汽车的安全性和可靠性，外界仍然存在疑问。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14bf4315/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Google%E6%B8%B8%E8%AF%B4%E5%86%85%E5%8D%8E%E8%BE%BE%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F11%2F0915224%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Google%E6%B8%B8%E8%AF%B4%E5%86%85%E5%8D%8E%E8%BE%BE%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB%E9%A9%BE%E9%A9%B6%E6%B1%BD%E8%BD%A6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F11%2F0915224%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091987722/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14bf4315/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101091987722/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14bf4315/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=esZ2x4kRjjo:FmrHJuO3CY0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=esZ2x4kRjjo:FmrHJuO3CY0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img bord